column1: #FORMAT=WebAnno TSV 3.2
#T_SP=webanno.custom.Referent|entity|infstat
#T_RL=webanno.custom.Coref|type|BT_webanno.custom.Referent
#Text=You 've had comics that have included actual people such as Richard Stallman .
#Text=What has been your reaction to meeting people you ’ve discussed or mentioned or made fun of , or gently poked in the comic ?
#Text=RM : It ’s extremely surreal .
#Text=And I mean just discovering that my , this is a normal person , and this is someone from my history books and I ’m sitting here eating food with them .
#Text=And that has not stopped being weird .
#Text=And a lot of the time I feel like I should be having more substantial conversation than I am .
#Text=I ’m almost at a loss because it 's such an enormous feeling .
#Text=It makes me realize why people act so weird when they meet me , because I might be the same to them .
#Text=So is there anyone you ’ve put in the comics that you ’d like to meet but have n’t ?
#Text=RM : Janeane Garofalo for a while now .
#Text=My fans have been acting out my comics and I was making them weird and the fans were still acting them out .
#Text=So I was just like , I ’m going to make one that is impossible for you to make happen and then that can be the standing challenge .
#Text=If someone can do that then I can start worrying about this again .
#Text=And so I had Janeane Garofalo jumping a motorcycle off of a crashing space station towards a volcanic island with dinosaurs while she is armed with a tranquilizer gun .
#Text=I figured that would be good .
#Text=The reason I mentioned her was because I ’ve been watching some of her movies and she ’s just adorable .
#Text=Somewhat on that topic , there was — I do n’t know if you saw it — there was a website that had a fake news article about a hundred xkcders commit suicide by imitating one of your comics .
#Text=RM : I read that , I forgot exactly what site it was maybe BBspot .
#Text=Note it was BBspot .
#Text=See
#Text=So that 's the sort of thing you 're thinking of in terms of people imitating things ?
#Text=RM : I generally do n’t worry about you know , that people are going to do something deadly because I mention it .
#Text=That would be bad but I do n’t think that would be my responsibility if that happened .
#Text=I do sort of wonder about is , people acting out something that has negative effects on the community .

#Text=If I put some kind of prank that in real life that would be mean-spirited or hurtful and if someone does that to someone famous and would lead to tension and bad feelings , then I would feel bad .
#Text=You did say on your blag at one point that “ But remember , I am not advocating doing anything dangerous unless it ’s really cool . ” .
